import React from "react" import {useHistory} from "react-router-dom" import NavBar from "../Nav" export default function NeedMoreCards({deckName, deckId, cardsLength}){ const history = useHistory() const navigation = {Home: "/", [deckName]: `/decks/${deckId}/`, Study: ""} return (

{deckName}: Study

Not Enough Cards


You need at least 3 cards to study with. There are only {cardsLength} cards in the deck.
